_sText:
Medium sized Gungame / fightyard map. 30 player spawn points with buyzones. Compiled with HDR lighting.

Players are spawned together at a different location each round. Each team has three possible start locations on the map, and one of these is chosen at the start of each round. Best not to tell new players about this simply for the confusion related humor value. 

Jernau's Maps site is at http://maps.playerofgames.net/
